>> source: Joy of Cooking
>> serves: 1.5 qts

Bring to a boil in a #large saucepan{} 3 cups @water{3%cups}.

Add and stir until dissolved @tea bags{7}, @dried hibiscus flowers{1/2%cup}, and @sugar{1/2%cup}.

Let stand ~{10%minutes}, then strain into a #pitcher{}. Stir in @ice water{3%cups}.

Pour over ice in #tall glasses. Garnish with @orange slices or raspberries{}.
